docs.lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES, Nov. 7 No one knows who did the shooting. Or why. Or how many times it will happen again on the shadow side of some low peak where the great birds swing low over brush-covered ridges and make fat targets against a cloudless sky.
docs.abstract: Interior Dept establishment of 53,000-acre sanctuary for birds, particularly Calif condors, within Los Padres Natl Forest noted (M)
